metadata.name: Virgo Constellation story
metadata.description:
Constellations NFT Club Constellations started in Greece around 3000 BC, and the names of heroes and animals from myths were pasted around

Virgo star story 
The story of Persephone, the daughter of Demeter, the goddess of the earth, is as follows. Persephone was a beautiful woman that captured the heart of Hades, the king of the underworld. In love with her beauty, Persephone, Hades kidnapped her and made her his wife. Persephone said that she had lived a decent life in the underworld, but she sometimes felt deep sorrow when she thought of the landscapes above. When her spring comes, her Virgo, rising into her eastern sky, is the figure of Persephone rising from the underworld.
